<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>InvestGrow - Virtual Trading Platform</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #0f3460;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    nav h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #e94560;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #f5f5f5;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #e94560;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #e94560;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 50px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      color: #e94560;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #e94560;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 30px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #c72d45;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #0f3460;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <nav>
    <h1>InvestGrow</h1>
    <div>
      <a href="/login">Login</a>
      <a href="/signup">Register</a>
      <a href="/stock/leaderboard">Leaderboard</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Trade Virtually. Learn Fearlessly.</h2>
    <p>Welcome to InvestGrow! Practice real-time stock trading in the Indian equity market using virtual money.
      Compete with others, manage your portfolio, and rank on the leaderboard. Start your trading journey risk-free!</p>
    <a href="/stock/portfolio" class="btn">Start Trading</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>üíº Portfolio Tracking</h3>
      <p>Track your virtual investments, gains, and losses in real-time. Manage your equity trades smartly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>üìà Real Market Data</h3>
      <p>Trade based on real Indian equity stock prices fetched live from the market. Analyze and invest smartly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>‚≠ê Leaderboard</h3>
      <p>Compete with fellow traders and climb the leaderboard based on your portfolio returns. Win exciting virtual
        rewards!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>üëÄ Watchlist</h3>
      <p>Add your favorite stocks to your watchlist and stay updated with their live prices and market movements.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 InvestGrow | Built for learning and practice purposes only.
  </footer>

</body>

</html>
